# 🤖 AgentID — KYA Protocol on Solana
## Complete Project Documentation

> **Repo:** [exactly-as-seen](file:///c:/Users/vg890/OneDrive/Desktop/agentid-kya-solana/exactly-as-seen) (GitHub: `Vishal4742/exactly-as-seen`)
> **Idea Doc:** [idea-2-agentid-kya-solana.md](file:///c:/Users/vg890/OneDrive/Desktop/agentid-kya-solana/idea-2-agentid-kya-solana.md)
> **Date:** March 8, 2026
> **Grant Target:** Solana Foundation via Superteam Earn — up to $10,000
> **Timeline:** 5-week MVP

---

## 1. Vision & Problem Statement

**AgentID** is the first Solana-native "Know Your Agent" (KYA) protocol. It gives every AI agent:

- A **verifiable on-chain identity** (soul-bound cNFT credential)
- A **reputation score** (0–1000) from tx history, uptime & human ratings
- **Autonomous payment capability** via x402 + USDC treasury
- An **immutable audit trail** of every action on Solana

### Why it matters

Every major player (Stripe, Visa, OpenAI, Google) launched AI agent identity frameworks in 2025 — but all are off-chain & Web2-native. ERC-8004 exists on Ethereum only. Solana (home of ai16z/ELIZA with 50k+ GitHub stars) has **zero on-chain agent identity layer**. AgentID fills this gap.

### India-specific angle

Indian AI freelance agencies need TDS (Tax Deducted at Source) compliance for agent-generated payments. AgentID stores GSTIN and PAN hash on-chain and auto-generates compliant invoices — a killer feature for the Superteam India grant.

---

## 2. Architecture Overview

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                         AGENTID STACK                            │
│                                                                  │
│  L1 IDENTITY     → Soul-bound cNFT via Metaplex Bubblegum       │
│  L2 REPUTATION   → Oracle-computed score (0–1000), on-chain      │
│  L3 PAYMENT      → x402 micropayments + USDC Treasury program   │
│  L4 SDK          → ELIZA plugin + TypeScript SDK + CPI calls     │
│                                                                  │
│  Stack: Anchor (Rust) | Next.js/Vite (React+TS) | Tailwind      │
│         Metaplex cNFT | Helius DAS | Arweave | Supabase         │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

